===Noun===
'''spam''' (plural: [[spams]])

# An unsolicited electronic message sent in bulk, e.g. by email or newsgroups.
#: ''I received 58 spams yesterday.''
# (''Collective noun'') Multiple unsolicited bulk electronic messages considered as an aggregate.
#: ''I get far too much spam.''

===Intransitive verb===
'''spam''' ([[spammed]], spammed)

# To send spam.

